idential buildings. This benefit, aimed at providing financial relief and encouraging tax compliance, applies only to self-occupied, purely residential properties. The move aligns with previous demands for tax concessions for older buildings as well.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/prayagraj-municipal-corporation-offers-25-tax-rebate-on-new-residential-buildings/130187381?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-41312/130187381.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}